<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="es">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0, maximum-scale=1.0">
<title>FitLink Global — Affiliate Onboarding</title>
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Playfair+Display:ital,wght@0,700;0,900;1,700&family=Lato:wght@300;400;700&family=Space+Mono:wght@400;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
<style>
  :root {
    --green: #344b48;
    --gold: #dac39b;
    --gray: #575250;
    --light-gold: #f0e6d3;
    --cream: #faf7f2;
    --dark: #1a2422;
  }
  * { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; }
  html, body { height: 100%; overflow: hidden; }
  body { font-family: 'Lato', sans-serif; background: var(--cream); display: flex; flex-direction: column; }

  @keyframes fadeUp {
    from { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(18px); }
    to   { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }
  }
  @keyframes shimmer {
    0%   { background-position: -200% center; }
    100% { background-position:  200% center; }
  }
  @keyframes pulse { 0%,100%{opacity:1} 50%{opacity:.5} }

  .fade-up { animation: fadeUp .45s ease forwards; }
  .gold-shimmer {
    background: linear-gradient(90deg, #dac39b, #f5e8cc, #dac39b);
    background-size: 200% auto;
    -webkit-background-clip: text;
    -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
    background-clip: text;
    animation: shimmer 3s linear infinite;
  }

  /* ── TOP NAV ── */
  #topnav {
    background: var(--green);
    padding: 10px 16px;
    display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: space-between;
    border-bottom: 2px solid rgba(218,195,155,.2);
    flex-shrink: 0; z-index: 100;
    gap: 10px;
  }
  .nav-brand { display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 8px; }
  .nav-dot   { width: 7px; height: 7px; border-radius: 50%; background: var(--gold); flex-shrink:0; }
  .nav-title { font-family: 'Space Mono', monospace; font-size: 10px; color: var(--gold); letter-spacing: .15em; }
  .nav-sub   { font-size: 9px; color: rgba(218,195,155,.4); margin-left: 4px; display:none; }
  @media(min-width:420px){ .nav-sub { display:inline; } }

  /* progress dots in topnav */
  #nav-dots { display: flex; gap: 5px; align-items: center; }
  .ndot {
    height: 3px; border-radius: 99px;
    background: rgba(218,195,155,.25);
    transition: all .3s ease; cursor: pointer;
    width: 20px;
  }
  .ndot.active { background: var(--gold); width: 32px; }

  /* ── SCROLL AREA ── */
  #scroll-area {
    flex: 1; overflow-y: auto; overflow-x: hidden;
    -webkit-overflow-scrolling: touch;
  }
  #scroll-area::-webkit-scrollbar { display: none; }

  /* ── BOTTOM NAV ── */
  #botnav {
    background: #fff;
    border-top: 1px solid rgba(52,75,72,.1);
    padding: 12px 20px;
    display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: center;
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }
  .nav-btn {
    background: var(--green); border: 1.5px solid var(--gold);
    color: var(--gold); padding: 9px 20px; border-radius: 99px;
    font-family: 'Space Mono', monospace; font-size: 10px;
    letter-spacing: .08em; cursor: pointer; transition: all .2s;
    -webkit-appearance: none;
  }
  .nav-btn:disabled {
    background: transparent;
    border-color: rgba(52,75,72,.2);
    color: rgba(52,75,72,.3);
    cursor: default;
  }
  .nav-btn:not(:disabled):active { transform: scale(.96); }

  /* section label */
  #section-label {
    font-family: 'Space Mono', monospace;
    font-size: 9px; color: var(--gray);
    letter-spacing: .1em; text-align: center;
  }

  /* ── SHARED ── */
  .section { padding: 40px 20px 60px; max-width: 700px; margin: 0 auto; }
  .section-tag {
    font-family: 'Space Mono', monospace; font-size: 10px;
    color: var(--gold); letter-spacing: .25em; margin-bottom: 14px;
  }
  .section-title {
    font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
    font-size: clamp(28px,6vw,46px); font-weight: 900;
    color: var(--green); line-height: 1.2; margin-bottom: 20px;
  }
  .section-body {
    font-size: 14px; color: var(--gray); line-height: 1.8;
  }
  .badge {
    font-size: 9px; font-weight: 700; letter-spacing: .12em;
    padding: 3px 9px; border-radius: 99px;
    background: var(--gold); color: var(--dark);
    font-family: 'Space Mono', monospace; display: inline-block;
  }
  .dark-card {
    background: var(--green); border-radius: 18px;
    padding: 28px 24px; margin-top: 24px;
  }
  .dark-card-title {
    font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
    font-size: clamp(16px,3vw,22px);
    color: var(--gold); font-weight: 700; font-style: italic;
    line-height: 1.5; margin-bottom: 14px;
  }

  /* ── WELCOME ── */
  #s0 { text-align: center; padding-top: 32px; }
  .stat-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(3,1fr); gap: 12px; max-width: 360px; margin: 24px auto 0; }
  .stat-box {
    background: rgba(52,75,72,.05);
    border: 1.5px solid rgba(52,75,72,.12);
    border-radius: 14px; padding: 16px 10px; text-align: center;
  }
  .stat-n { font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif; font-size: 32px; font-weight: 900; color: var(--green); }
  .stat-l { font-size: 10px; color: var(--gray); font-family: 'Space Mono', monospace; letter-spacing: .1em; }
  .pill-row { display: flex; flex-wrap: wrap; gap: 10px; justify-content: center; margin: 24px 0; }
  .pill {
    background: var(--green); color: var(--gold);
    border-radius: 99px; padding: 7px 16px;
    font-size: 11px; font-family: 'Space Mono', monospace;
  }

  /* ── STORY ── */
  .timeline-line {
    position: relative; padding-left: 28px;
  }
  .timeline-line::before {
    content: ''; position: absolute; left: 7px; top: 8px; bottom: 8px;
    width: 2px;
    background: linear-gradient(to bottom, transparent, var(--gold), transparent);
  }
  .tl-item { position: relative; margin-bottom: 32px; }
  .tl-dot {
    position: absolute; left: -24px; top: 5px;
    width: 14px; height: 14px; border-radius: 50%;
    background: var(--gold); border: 3px solid var(--cream);
    z-index: 1;
  }
  .tl-year {
    font-family: 'Space Mono', monospace; font-size: 10px;
    color: var(--gold); letter-spacing: .15em; margin-bottom: 6px;
  }
  .tl-title {
    font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif; font-size: 18px;
    font-weight: 700; color: var(--green); margin-bottom: 8px;
  }

  /* ── PORTFOLIO ── */
  .cat-tabs { display: flex; gap: 8px; margin-bottom: 24px; flex-wrap: wrap; }
  .cat-tab {
    background: rgba(52,75,72,.06);
    border: 1.5px solid rgba(52,75,72,.2);
    color: var(--green); border-radius: 99px;
    padding: 8px 16px; font-family: 'Space Mono', monospace;
    font-size: 10px; letter-spacing: .08em; cursor: pointer;
    transition: all .2s; -webkit-appearance: none;
    display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 6px;
  }
  .cat-tab.active {
    background: var(--green); border-color: var(--gold); color: var(--gold);
  }
  .partner-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fill, minmax(150px, 1fr));
    gap: 12px;
  }
  .partner-card {
    background: rgba(52,75,72,.06);
    border: 1.5px solid rgba(52,75,72,.15);
    border-radius: 14px; padding: 14px;
    cursor: pointer; transition: all .22s;
  }
  .partner-card:active {
    background: var(--green);
    border-color: var(--gold);
    transform: scale(.97);
  }
  .p-emoji { font-size: 22px; margin-bottom: 8px; }
  .p-name  { font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif; font-size: 15px; font-weight: 700; color: var(--green); margin-bottom: 4px; }
  .p-tag-line { font-size: 10px; color: var(--gray); line-height: 1.5; }

  /* ── MODAL ── */
  #modal-overlay {
    position: fixed; inset: 0;
    background: rgba(26,36,34,.88);
    display: none; align-items: flex-end; justify-content: center;
    z-index: 999;
    backdrop-filter: blur(6px);
    -webkit-backdrop-filter: blur(6px);
  }
  #modal-overlay.open { display: flex; }
  #modal-box {
    background: var(--green);
    border-radius: 24px 24px 0 0;
    padding: 28px 24px 40px;
    width: 100%; max-width: 600px;
    border: 1.5px solid var(--gold);
    border-bottom: none;
    max-height: 88vh; overflow-y: auto;
    animation: fadeUp .3s ease;
  }
  #modal-box::-webkit-scrollbar { display: none; }
  .modal-header { display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: flex-start; margin-bottom: 20px; }
  .modal-close {
    background: rgba(255,255,255,.12); border: none;
    color: var(--light-gold); border-radius: 50%;
    width: 32px; height: 32px; font-size: 16px;
    cursor: pointer; flex-shrink: 0; -webkit-appearance: none;
  }
  .modal-name { font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif; font-size: 22px; color: var(--gold); font-weight: 700; }
  .modal-desc { color: var(--light-gold); font-size: 13px; line-height: 1.75; margin-bottom: 18px; }
  .modal-section-label {
    font-family: 'Space Mono', monospace; font-size: 9px;
    color: var(--gold); letter-spacing: .12em; margin-bottom: 10px;
  }
  .tag-chips { display: flex; flex-wrap: wrap; gap: 8px; margin-bottom: 18px; }
  .tag-chip {
    font-size: 11px; background: rgba(218,195,155,.15);
    color: var(--light-gold); border-radius: 99px; padding: 4px 12px;
  }
  .pitch-box {
    background: rgba(218,195,155,.1);
    border-radius: 12px; padding: 14px;
    border-left: 3px solid var(--gold);
  }
  .pitch-text { color: var(--cream); font-size: 13px; line-height: 1.65; font-style: italic; }

  /* ── STRATEGIES ── */
  .strat-card {
    background: rgba(52,75,72,.05);
    border: 1.5px solid rgba(52,75,72,.15);
    border-radius: 16px; overflow: hidden; margin-bottom: 12px;
  }
  .strat-header {
    padding: 16px 20px; cursor: pointer;
    display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: center;
    -webkit-user-select: none; user-select: none;
  }
  .strat-header:active { background: rgba(52,75,72,.08); }
  .strat-left { display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 12px; }
  .strat-emoji { font-size: 26px; }
  .strat-title { font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif; font-size: 16px; font-weight: 700; color: var(--green); }
  .strat-subtitle { font-size: 11px; color: var(--gray); margin-top: 2px; }
  .strat-right { display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 8px; }
  .strat-arrow { font-size: 18px; color: var(--green); transition: transform .25s; display: inline-block; }
  .strat-body {
    padding: 0 20px 20px;
    border-top: 1px solid rgba(52,75,72,.1);
    display: none;
  }
  .strat-desc { font-size: 13px; color: var(--gray); line-height: 1.75; margin: 14px 0; }
  .step-row { display: flex; gap: 10px; align-items: flex-start; margin-bottom: 10px; }
  .step-num {
    min-width: 22px; height: 22px; border-radius: 50%;
    background: var(--green); color: var(--gold);
    font-size: 10px; font-weight: 700; font-family: 'Space Mono', monospace;
    display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; flex-shrink: 0;
  }
  .step-text { font-size: 12px; color: var(--dark); line-height: 1.6; padding-top: 2px; }
  .example-box {
    background: var(--green); border-radius: 10px; padding: 12px 14px; margin-top: 12px;
  }
  .example-label { font-size: 9px; font-family: 'Space Mono', monospace; color: var(--gold); letter-spacing: .1em; }
  .example-text  { font-size: 12px; color: var(--light-gold); margin-top: 4px; line-height: 1.5; }

  /* ── ROADMAP ── */
  .rm-tabs { display: flex; gap: 8px; flex-wrap: wrap; margin-bottom: 24px; }
  .rm-tab {
    background: rgba(52,75,72,.06); border: 1.5px solid rgba(52,75,72,.15);
    color: var(--green); border-radius: 99px; padding: 7px 14px;
    font-family: 'Space Mono', monospace; font-size: 10px;
    letter-spacing: .06em; cursor: pointer; -webkit-appearance: none;
    transition: all .2s;
  }
  .rm-tab.active { background: var(--green); border-color: var(--gold); color: var(--gold); }
  .rm-card {
    background: var(--green); border-radius: 20px;
    padding: 32px 24px; text-align: center; min-height: 180px;
    transition: all .3s;
  }
  .rm-icon   { font-size: 42px; margin-bottom: 12px; }
  .rm-day    { font-family: 'Space Mono', monospace; font-size: 10px; color: var(--gold); letter-spacing: .2em; margin-bottom: 10px; }
  .rm-title  { font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif; font-size: 22px; color: var(--gold); font-weight: 700; margin-bottom: 12px; }
  .rm-desc   { color: var(--light-gold); font-size: 13px; line-height: 1.75; max-width: 400px; margin: 0 auto; }
  .principles-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(2,1fr); gap: 12px; margin-top: 28px; }
  .princ-card {
    background: rgba(52,75,72,.05); border-radius: 14px;
    padding: 16px; border: 1.5px solid rgba(52,75,72,.12);
  }
  .princ-icon  { font-size: 24px; margin-bottom: 8px; }
  .princ-title { font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif; font-size: 14px; font-weight: 700; color: var(--green); margin-bottom: 5px; }
  .princ-desc  { font-size: 11px; color: var(--gray); line-height: 1.6; }

  /* ── MANIFESTO ── */
  #s5 { text-align: center; }
  .manifesto-list { text-align: left; max-width: 500px; margin: 0 auto 32px; }
  .manifesto-item { display: flex; gap: 14px; align-items: flex-start; margin-bottom: 14px; opacity: 0; }
  .manifesto-item.revealed { animation: fadeUp .5s ease forwards; }
  .m-dot { width: 6px; height: 6px; border-radius: 50%; background: var(--gold); margin-top: 7px; flex-shrink: 0; }
  .m-text { font-size: 14px; color: var(--gray); line-height: 1.75; }
  .manifesto-quote {
    font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
    font-size: clamp(15px,3vw,20px); color: var(--gold);
    font-style: italic; line-height: 1.55; margin-bottom: 20px;
  }
  .market-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(3,1fr); gap: 12px; margin-top: 20px; }
  .market-item { border-top: 2px solid var(--gold); padding-top: 10px; }
  .market-n { font-family: 'Space Mono', monospace; font-size: 13px; color: var(--gold); font-weight: 700; }
  .market-l { font-size: 10px; color: rgba(218,195,155,.6); }
  .final-box {
    background: var(--green); border-radius: 18px;
    padding: 24px 20px; margin-top: 24px;
    border: 2px solid var(--gold);
  }
  .final-tag   { font-family: 'Space Mono', monospace; font-size: 9px; color: var(--gold); letter-spacing: .2em; margin-bottom: 12px; }
  .final-title { font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif; font-size: 18px; color: var(--cream); font-weight: 700; margin-bottom: 10px; }
  .final-desc  { font-size: 12px; color: rgba(218,195,155,.7); line-height: 1.7; margin-bottom: 16px; }
  .final-pills { display: flex; flex-wrap: wrap; gap: 10px; justify-content: center; }
  .final-pill  { background: rgba(218,195,155,.15); border-radius: 10px; padding: 8px 14px; font-size: 11px; color: var(--gold); font-family: 'Space Mono', monospace; }
</style>
</head>
<body>

<!-- TOP NAV -->
<div id="topnav">
  <div class="nav-brand">
    <div class="nav-dot"></div>
    <span class="nav-title">FITLINK GLOBAL</span>
    <span class="nav-sub">AFFILIATE ONBOARDING</span>
  </div>
  <div id="nav-dots"></div>
</div>

<!-- SCROLL AREA -->
<div id="scroll-area">

  <!-- S0: WELCOME -->
  <div id="s0" class="section fade-up">
    <div class="section-tag">BIENVENIDO AL EQUIPO</div>
    <div class="section-title">
      Estás a punto de<br>
      <span class="gold-shimmer">vender el futuro</span><br>
      del fitness
    </div>
    <p class="section-body" style="max-width:480px;margin:0 auto 24px;">
      Este sistema te va a dar todo lo que necesitas para representar a FitLink Global con autoridad, confianza y resultados. No es un catálogo. Es una ventaja competitiva.
    </p>
    <div class="pill-row">
      <div class="pill">20+ Productos & Servicios</div>
      <div class="pill">4 Continentes</div>
      <div class="pill">Hardware · Software · Diseño</div>
    </div>
    <div class="stat-grid">
      <div class="stat-box"><div class="stat-n">20+</div><div class="stat-l">Partners</div></div>
      <div class="stat-box"><div class="stat-n">6</div><div class="stat-l">Módulos</div></div>
      <div class="stat-box"><div class="stat-n">∞</div><div class="stat-l">Oportunidad</div></div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- S1: STORY -->
  <div id="s1" class="section fade-up" style="display:none;">
    <div class="section-tag">LA HISTORIA</div>
    <div class="section-title">No somos una distribuidora. Somos un <em>ecosistema</em>.</div>
    <div class="timeline-line">
      <div class="tl-item">
        <div class="tl-dot"></div>
        <div class="tl-year">EL ORIGEN</div>
        <div class="tl-title">Una brecha en el mercado</div>
        <p class="section-body">FitLink nació de observar que el sector fitness global carecía de un puente real entre la innovación tecnológica y los operadores de negocio. Las mejores soluciones no llegaban a quienes más las necesitaban.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="tl-item">
        <div class="tl-dot"></div>
        <div class="tl-year">LA VISIÓN</div>
        <div class="tl-title">Más que distribución</div>
        <p class="section-body">Desde el primer día, FitLink se posicionó como socio estratégico. No vendemos productos: conectamos soluciones con problemas reales, construimos relaciones de largo plazo, y elevamos toda la industria.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="tl-item">
        <div class="tl-dot"></div>
        <div class="tl-year">LA RED</div>
        <div class="tl-title">20+ partners de primer nivel</div>
        <p class="section-body">Construimos un portfolio cuidadosamente seleccionado: hardware de vanguardia, software que genera datos accionables, y servicios que transforman espacios en experiencias. Europa, Latinoamérica, el mundo.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="tl-item">
        <div class="tl-dot"></div>
        <div class="tl-year">HOY</div>
        <div class="tl-title">Donde tú entras</div>
        <p class="section-body">FitLink opera en DACH, España y Latinoamérica con una red de revendedores que multiplica el impacto. Tú eres la extensión de esa red. Tu éxito es nuestro éxito.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="dark-card" style="text-align:center;">
      <div class="dark-card-title">"El fitness no es solo industria. Es el espejo donde la sociedad refleja sus valores de salud, longevidad y bienestar."</div>
      <div style="font-size:11px;color:rgba(218,195,155,.55);font-family:'Space Mono',monospace;">— FitLink Global · Berlin</div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- S2: PORTFOLIO -->
  <div id="s2" class="section fade-up" style="display:none;">
    <div class="section-tag">EL PORTFOLIO</div>
    <div class="section-title">Cada producto,<br>una oportunidad.</div>
    <p class="section-body" style="margin-bottom:24px;">Toca cualquier tarjeta para ver el argumento de venta completo.</p>
    <div class="cat-tabs" id="cat-tabs">
      <button class="cat-tab active" data-cat="hardware" onclick="switchCat('hardware',this)">🔧 Hardware <span style="opacity:.6;font-size:9px;">(11)</span></button>
      <button class="cat-tab" data-cat="software" onclick="switchCat('software',this)">💻 Software <span style="opacity:.6;font-size:9px;">(7)</span></button>
      <button class="cat-tab" data-cat="services" onclick="switchCat('services',this)">✨ Servicios <span style="opacity:.6;font-size:9px;">(2)</span></button>
    </div>
    <div id="partner-grid" class="partner-grid"></div>
    <div style="margin-top:24px;background:rgba(52,75,72,.04);border-radius:14px;padding:16px;border:1.5px dashed rgba(52,75,72,.2);text-align:center;">
      <p style="font-size:12px;color:var(--gray);">El portfolio crece constantemente. Como revendedor, recibirás actualizaciones anticipadas de nuevos productos antes del lanzamiento oficial.</p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- S3: STRATEGIES -->
  <div id="s3" class="section fade-up" style="display:none;">
    <div class="section-tag">ESTRATEGIAS DE VENTA</div>
    <div class="section-title">No hay una sola forma de ganar. Hay cinco.</div>
    <p class="section-body" style="margin-bottom:28px;">Toca cada estrategia para ver el playbook completo.</p>
    <div id="strat-list"></div>
  </div>

  <!-- S4: ROADMAP -->
  <div id="s4" class="section fade-up" style="display:none;">
    <div class="section-tag">TU CAMINO</div>
    <div class="section-title">Los primeros 60 días<br>lo cambian todo.</div>
    <div class="rm-tabs" id="rm-tabs"></div>
    <div class="rm-card" id="rm-card"></div>
    <div class="principles-grid">
      <div class="princ-card"><div class="princ-icon">🎯</div><div class="princ-title">Especialización</div><div class="princ-desc">Un mercado primero. Profundidad antes que amplitud.</div></div>
      <div class="princ-card"><div class="princ-icon">🤝</div><div class="princ-title">Relación primero</div><div class="princ-desc">La confianza de hoy es la comisión de mañana.</div></div>
      <div class="princ-card"><div class="princ-icon">📊</div><div class="princ-title">Habla con datos</div><div class="princ-desc">ROI y casos de éxito. Los números cierran puertas.</div></div>
      <div class="princ-card"><div class="princ-icon">🔗</div><div class="princ-title">Piensa en combos</div><div class="princ-desc">Dos productos juntos valen más que dos veces uno.</div></div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- S5: MANIFESTO -->
  <div id="s5" class="section fade-up" style="display:none;">
    <div class="section-tag">EL MANIFESTO</div>
